    <item>
      <title>Launching a new course at TUM - Software Engineering Lab</title>
      <link>https://hofbi.github.io/post/software-lab/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Apr 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://hofbi.github.io/post/software-lab/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We are launching a new course at the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering, Technical University of Munich, Germany.
The course is called Software Engineering Lab and is part of the Bachelor in Electrical and Computer Engineering (BSEI).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find all details about the course: &lt;a href=&#34;https://hofbi.github.io/teaching/software-lab/&#34;&gt;Software Engineering Lab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check the course page at the chair: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ce.cit.tum.de/lmt&#34;&gt;Chair of Media Technology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read our publication: &lt;a href=&#34;https://hofbi.github.io/publication/software_lab&#34;&gt;Teaching Software Engineering As Programming Over Time&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
